#: big-parental-controls/usr/bin/big-supervised-indicator:58
#: big-parental-controls/usr/bin/big-supervised-indicator:83
msgid "Parental controls are active"
msgstr "O controle parental está ativo"

#: big-parental-controls/usr/bin/big-supervised-indicator:65
msgid "What does this mean?"
msgstr "O que isso significa?"

#: big-parental-controls/usr/bin/big-supervised-indicator:70
msgid "I need help"
msgstr "Preciso de ajuda"

#: big-parental-controls/usr/bin/big-supervised-indicator:85
msgid ""
"A responsible adult set up protections on this account to help keep you "
"safe.\n"
"\n"
"Some apps may be blocked and there may be time limits for using the "
"computer.\n"
"\n"
"If you think something is wrong, talk to a trusted adult."
msgstr ""
"Um adulto responsável configurou proteções nesta conta para ajudar a manter "
"você seguro.\n"
"\n"
"Alguns aplicativos podem estar bloqueados e pode haver limites de tempo para "
"usar o computador.\n"
"\n"
"Se você acha que algo está errado, converse com um adulto de confiança."

#: big-parental-controls/usr/bin/big-supervised-indicator:92
msgid "About parental controls"
msgstr "Sobre o controle parental"

#: big-parental-controls/usr/bin/big-supervised-indicator:102
msgid "Need help?"
msgstr "Precisa de ajuda?"

#: big-parental-controls/usr/bin/big-supervised-indicator:104
msgid ""
"Talk to a trusted adult — a parent, teacher, or relative.\n"
"\n"
"You can also call:\n"
"• CVV 188 — free emotional support, 24 hours\n"
"• Disque 100 — report rights violations\n"
"• SaferNet — safernet.org.br\n"
"\n"
"These services are free and confidential."
msgstr ""
"Converse com um adulto de confiança — pai, mãe, professor ou parente.\n"
"\n"
"Você também pode ligar:\n"
"• CVV 188 — apoio emocional gratuito, 24 horas\n"
"• Disque 100 — denuncie violações de direitos\n"
"• SaferNet — safernet.org.br\n"
"\n"
"Esses serviços são gratuitos e sigilosos."

